This function returns ( mpz ** <i>a</i> ) % <i>b</i>.
For example, <tt> Mpz(2)-&gt;powm(10,42); </tt> would return <tt>16</tt>
since 2 to the power of 10 is 1024 and 1024 modulo 42 is 16.
