<tt>MIME.encode_qp</tt> - Encode string using <tt>quoted-printable</tt> transfer encoding
<p>
<dt><encaps>SYNTAX</encaps><dd>
<tt>string encode_qp(string <i>data</i>, void|int <i>no_linebreaks</i>);<br>
